      <description>&lt;p&gt;My flat mate&amp;rsquo;s VISTA decided to corrupt itself. Rather than telling her to bin it and get a new one I used an Ubuntu live CD to view the hard drive and burn a back up onto DVDs.&lt;/p&gt;
